Harry and Meghan have attempted to use Sussex Royal branding since stepping down from senior royal duties, despite being banned from using the word royal. A source told royal expert Robert Jobson that this upset William, who found it "insulting" towards the Queen. The source said: "That was it for William – he felt they’d blindsided the Queen in such an insulting and disrespectful way." Kensington Palace declined to comment.  FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES... 